{"tid":1995174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞刺針：遙距抗體檢查都拎到醫生紙？","createTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T05:15:11.000Z","uid":42582,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9af79837b24e9846f9ca8991ebf6a0ff03b82747","tid":1995174,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"新聞刺針：【遙距抗體檢測都拎到醫生紙？】<br />\n<br />\n上星期報道過，有醫療機構出售的新型肺炎抗體測試產品不適合家用、準確度亦成疑。記者追查發現，有私家診所、體檢中心叫求診人士用這類產品喺屋企檢驗，唔駛見醫生，就可獲發有醫生印鑑的收據。<br />\n<br />\n醫生憑抗體測試，就發出醫生印章的「收據」，有沒有問題？記者問過中大醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌、醫學會前主席蔡堅意見，又搵咗涉事醫生、體檢中心回應，睇下佢地點講。<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1542638889242480&amp;id=153300521509664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1542638889242480%26id%3D153300521509664&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=176052d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1542638889242480&amp;id=153300521509664</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有線又撚個肥鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c73090766ec65a3d0d8d29a53661a1ee4905a08","tid":1995174,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"邊位？個樣同談吐都好有獸醫feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c5391499255e3879628b246c89acf7acdaae08","tid":1995174,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c73090766ec65a3d0d8d29a53661a1ee4905a08","tid":1995174,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"邊位？個樣同談吐都好有獸醫feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"據報道講，受測者連醫生真人樣貌都未見過